{
  "stem": "802.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They were much better off than in Warsaw, because the starvation at this point-- in the beginning, already-- the starvation was really awful.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I want to talk about it some more, not only about the starvation, but the influx of people from neighboring towns, from all over in Poland and Europe, too.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I didn't finish my thought, but I don't even remember exactly what it was.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I guess it doesn't matter.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We were very fortunate in that our building was incorporated into the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "In other words, the ghetto-- our building was in the ghetto, because we lived in Jewish quarters.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So in that, we were extremely fortunate because we did not have to give up our apartment.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So we had some roots still.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But neighbors-- not neighbors, relatives of my mother, who lived in a small town not too far from Warsaw, were expelled from their little-- it was almost a village or a tiny town, a shtetl, and they moved in with us.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And at one point, there may have been about 18 people in this small apartment that was larger than on Mila Street, but it was still small.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And then I don't remember what happened to them.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They just disappeared.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "You know, one by one, or maybe they moved.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I don't remember with precision.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I could make up something, but I don't want to.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "You know, I want to be honest about it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So they just disappeared.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "What were the conditions?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "People from all over Poland, that is Jewish people from various shtetls, villages, towns, were made to come to Poland.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And there were no horses.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And, of course, who had a car?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Very few people had cars.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And so they were dragging their possessions in wagons.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
